{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Vilnius{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, and he\rquote d been \endash  only recently found out \endash  he\rquote d been recruited into the Tsar\rquote s Army, by the Cossacks, actually. His pa
rents were shot by the Germans in the First World War, that\rquote 
s all I know about them. And he was a carpenter by trade, and came over when he was about 20, in his early twenties, and started as a janitor, a caretaker, and then began to do up property and began to buy property. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12480245 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 
But when [my mother] was born, they were still living in the basement, as the caretaker. Her mother came by herself when she was 15, around 15, from a very very poor little village in Belaruse \endash  what is now Belaruse \endash  and she went out
