 and it was not a very happy one. He was quite a lot older than she was. So she was married off, and she never worked after that. She was a h
ousewife. And they only had three children. She had several abortions, I found out later. And only girls, to my grandfather\rquote s disgust! So that was that.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 And your mother\rquote s side, was that also actively religious, or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12480245\charrsid4223568 Leonore:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 No. My grandfather w
as unusual. He became quite secularised. He was almost illiterate, and he kept all his accounts in his head, but he was very bright, and he got to know cultured people, especially through banks and financial dealings around 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Boston{\*\xmlclose} - and {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Boston{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 was, you know, is a very cultural city - and he used to go to museums and find out things, and he bought a gramophone. So theirs was a more comfortable, more secularised household. My grandmother was very religious. She was completely illiterate, just ab
out, except in Yiddish, a little bit of Yiddish. And she did these Friday night rituals and that sort of thing, but it was fairly laid back, I think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 But in your childhood, there weren\rquote t those Friday night rituals?
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12480245\charrsid4223568 Leonore:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 No. No.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 
