u think was Jewish about the home? If there were no rituals, can you try and describe what you felt was Jewish about it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12480245\charrsid4223568 Leonore:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 
Certainly the emphasis on education and books and learning, very very strong. And when I was seven, the War broke out, and so before then, there had been refugees coming from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Europe{\*\xmlclose}
, and my parents took some in, and they were very involved with them, and we were very aware of what was going on, right from really early, and that\rquote s probably one of the biggest influences on my life. That was the Holocaust \endash 
 what is now called The Holocaust.
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
