{\*\xmlclose}, and not trying, giving up in the more mainstream. And he was one of the founders of Albert Einstein College of Medicine, which was founded by {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Yeshiva
{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}University{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}.
\par 
