\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 So do you think that she\rquote 
d forgotten those ideas when you were young, when you were a child? Or did she convey some of them to you?
