d never been to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}France{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, and to this day, I regret I can\rquote t speak French really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 There were all these other members of the family around, but were th
