 but she too, she had worked in Woolworths, had had to leave school at 16, had w
orked in Woolworths, put this pig of a husband through Medical School, he became, God help us, a psychiatrist! But she was so bright, and such a sparky - she was a wonderful woman. I was very very fond of her. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12480245 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 But as far as ambitions and so on, no, no, there couldn\rquote 
