League of Women Voters, she was running this, running that, and people would come to her. She was part of an interfaith group that did a sit-in - with black [people] \endash  through the churches \endash 
 and they did a sit-in in the local drugstore, and all these things.
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
