So eventually she decided to retrain. She did a some psychology, and she then went on to do a Doctor of Education at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Columbia{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, and got trained - it was in the early days of Marriage Counselling. By that time, I had left home, by the time she was fully trained, but we talked about it quite a lot. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid12846783 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12846783\charrsid4223568 
