 Ernie Kaufman, Jay Schulman and people like that. And I made quite close friends with a Greek graduate student, who later emigrated to the States, and she now works in the American government, she\rquote 
s an economist. So there were a few people like that. And, of course, I was still living with my American friend. And sh
