variety of politics. And the whole Politics Department was very lively. Bob McKenzie, that was the other one. Intellectually, it was very exciting. But there was absolutely no room for gender in there, so that split was getting worse and wider and wider f
or me, because also, of course, by that time I\rquote d met David.
